Package com.i2group.disco.infostore.importer

Contains utility classes that generate well-formed origin and provenance values for use during Information Store and Solr index ingestion.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OriginIdGenerator
    Generates values for the ORIGIN_ID_HASH and ORIGIN_ID_KEYS columns of provenance tables in the Information Store.
    RetrievalBlockDataGenerator
    Generates values for the RETRIEVAL_BLOCK_DATA columns of provenance tables in the Information Store, from values in the RETRIEVAL_BLOCK_TEMPLATE column of the INGESTION_SOURCES table.
    SolrProvenanceBuilder
    A utility class for building the provenance and record history strings to use in the Solr index of an Information Store.
    TemplateReferenceExtractor
    A utility class for determining whether strings in templates are references to values in columns (specified by $(COLUMN_NAME)) or constant values.
    TemplateReferenceExtractor.ColumnReferenceOrConstantValue
    A descriptor of whether a string in a template is a constant value (in which case it requires no further processing), or a reference to a value in a column (in which case it should be substituted for the value).

Package com.i2group.disco.infostore.importer Description
